Free accommodation
According to the Grey Leaf, a mage who can help in the search for the artifact has taken up residence in the lodging to the west of the mine area. The mage very rarely leaves his haven, so it is advisable to go to his camp.
#subobj 1
Come to the Free People
To get to the accommodation, go through the canyon in the center of the mine area and then turn west.
#subobj 2
Kill the tigers
The accommodation is under attack by snow tigers! You need to help the residents.